The experimental setup used in our experiments includes:
- Two scintillation counters S1 and S2;
- Three plastic scintillation detectors;
- A collimator;
- The target is made of natural tantalum foil with a thickness of 0.1 mm, placed between the first pair of scintillation counters;
- The trigger system consists of four scintillation counters T1-T4.
